
Normal CMake installation process, e.g.:

cd <path to code>/build/
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=debug -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=<prefix> ..
make
# opt. run unit tests
make test
# opt. create doxygen documentation
make doc
# opt. static code analysis
make cppcheck
# install
make install

To generate a coverage report chose "coverage" as CMake build type and do

make
make test
make coverage
